Name: AdFormat
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
TEXT / text
IMAGE / image
DYNAMIC_IMAGE / dynamic_image
FLASH / flash
VIDEO / video
HTML / html
AUDIO / audio
COMPOSITE / composite
PRINT / print
Notes: The ad type.

Name: AdGroupId
Notes: The ID of the AdGroup.

Name: AdNetworkType1
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
SEARCH / Search Network
CONTENT / Display Network
Notes: First level network type.

Name: AdNetworkType2
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / unknown
SEARCH / Google search
SEARCH_PARTNERS / Search partners
CONTENT / Display Network
Notes: Second level network type (includes search partners).

Name: CampaignId
Notes: The ID of the Campaign.

Name: CityCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the city Location associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: ClickType
Enum Values:
URL_CLICKS / Headline
CALLS / Phone calls
OTHER / Other
PRODUCT_EXTENSION_CLICKS / Product plusbox offer
SITELINKS / Sitelink
PRODUCT_LISTING_AD_CLICKS / Product listing ad
GET_DIRECTIONS / Driving direction
OFFER_PRINTS / Print offer
BREADCRUMBS / Breadcrumbs
CALL_TRACKING / Manually dialed phone calls
MOBILE_CALL_TRACKING / Mobile phone calls
LOCATION_EXPANSION / Get location details
UNKNOWN / unknown
Notes: The Impressions field will reflect how often the ad was served with that click type available. Since ads can serve with multiple click types displayed, impressions may be double counted and the totals may not be accurate.

Name: CountryCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the country Location associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: CreativeId
Notes: ID of the ad.

Name: CriteriaId
Notes: The Criterion ID.

Name: CriteriaParameters
Notes: Descriptive string for the Criterion. In the Destination URL report, this field behaves as a segment.

Name: Date
Notes: The date formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: Device
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / Other
DESKTOP / Computers
HIGH_END_MOBILE / Mobile devices with full browsers
TABLET / Tablets with full browsers
Notes: Device type where the impression was shown.

Name: GclId
Notes: The Google Click ID.

Name: MetroCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the metro area Location associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: MonthOfYear
Enum Values:
JANUARY / January
FEBRUARY / February
MARCH / March
APRIL / April
MAY / May
JUNE / June
JULY / July
AUGUST / August
SEPTEMBER / September
OCTOBER / October
NOVEMBER / November
DECEMBER / December
Notes: The name of the month of the year, e.g., "December".

Name: Page
Notes: Page number in search results where the ad was shown.

Name: RegionCriteriaId
Notes: ID of the region Location associated with the impression. You can look up the corresponding name and other information using LocationCriterionService.

Name: Slot
Enum Values:
SearchRhs / Google search: Side
SearchTop / Google search: Top
SearchOther / Google search: Other
Content / Google Display Network
AfsTop / Search partners: Top
AfsOther / Search partners: Other
Unknown /
Notes: The position of the Ad.

Name: UserListId
Notes: The ID of the UserList (audience).
